            <title><![CDATA[Ball toss]]></title>
            <link>https://igorcasmarques.github.io/micro-blog/ball-toss</link>
            <guid>https://igorcasmarques.github.io/micro-blog/ball-toss</guid>
            <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[This is my peak.]]></description>
